t the moment is really forcing people to rethink where their energy comes from, and I think people are gravitating more and more towards renewable technology. And also to reduce the dependency that we have on the grid, which in many parts of the world is aging quite rapidly.\"</p><p>The car's five-day trip was backed by Easee and Renault.</p></body>",
